text: Diana Filipova (born 11 July 1971) is a Bulgarian badminton player. She competed in women's doubles at the 1992 Summer Olympics in Barcelona. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian female badminton players Category:Olympic badminton players of Bulgaria Category:Badminton players at the 1992 Summer Olympics
